00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:09.150
higher because we keep
pumping it out.

00:13:09.150 --> 00:13:12.390
And so sodium, if you let it
go down its concentration

00:13:12.390 --> 00:13:14.070
gradient, it would go back in.

00:13:14.070 --> 00:13:18.490
And so maybe right here you have
some sodium going down,

00:13:18.490 --> 00:13:21.830
its concentration gradient going
back in, and then when

00:13:21.830 --> 00:13:24.120
that goes in, that you can
almost imagine it's some type

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:28.540
of a rotating door, it makes
